values: Chris reminded me that I haven't written in this thing for awhile...so this is what i am doing...  Allyson rocks my socks...Chris is my best friend...who never calls me anymore...and we are not allowed to hang out anymore because bobby is a jerkoff...and chris...i don't even know if he wants to hang out with me anymore, and he made allyson bleed....and he licked off his hand...allyson...chris has rabies....and he is laughing profusely....and he is getting very angry...i think he will kill me...but i guess i can wait....i don't know what it is....chris and allyson are having a nerd talk... a nerd talk is what they are talking...nerds...complete nerds....allyson is an eye whore....what does that mean?  allyson says she is not an eye whore..but an ass whore....she likes it in the ass....chris believes that both statements are true...in the eye and in the ass....chris is getting told off by esmerelda....i like chris' glasses....allyson....chris....allyson....chris....i don't like anal sex....  I watched Little Mermaid last nite!  IT ROCKED! G2G!

haha to all those biatches who didn't think that we would win that contest...we did!  not only did we win 3 tickets (which was supposed to be 2 tickets) we got 3 backstage passes to see ashlee simpson...omg!!  we were frickin' out...goes to show them asses who didn't think we could do it...afterwards we went to bennigans...and ate...and ate....but amber didn't eat cuz there was no alfredo sauce for her noodles...she was bummed but then she tried that meat loaf shit...which she wouldn't even touch....that guy billy who was our waiter was totally hitting on us....he was aight...he had a huge lump on the side of his head...with his pooey VOOTON!  lol...bobby wasn't really that happy that we won...."you're going to miss my baseball game"!  aw well....he'll get over it...he's in south texas with cameron at the current time...and me and andrea are eating at schlotzsky's....and playing on the intranet...lol....we might look at those phat condos down the road...i had a good day...omg i saw the notebook last nite...and cried like a little baby....i kinda miss bobby....actually i do....i love him...well i guess till next time....

well i do believe that he is leaving today, i think after lunch...which sucks...i really hope he has fun...part of me wants him to have a good time...and the other part of me (who just happens to  be a bitch) wants him to have such a miserable time because he left me...but i shouldn't feel that way...we are going to win that ashlee simpson contest...2 free tickets... bobby said we won't win, but i think we have a chance...we are going to have fun...we really are...i just hope we can make our iron on transfers by then....ok...well i guess i'm outtie...until next time

Life goes by quickly enough without you rushing through it in an enormous hurry.  Talk about your daily stress with your beloved, and then let it go.  Don't look back; the future's far more interesting.

THIS WAS MY HOROSC0PE FOR THE DAY!

sublime is what Mrs. Bassett described the feeling you get when you feel at complete bliss...and that's what i feel right now... things with me and bobby are great...i just feel like driving out in the country and breathing in all the fresh air...*SIGH*  Gosh, I love that guy...he makes me smile...I think that's what i realized yesterday...i do cause much drama in my relationship, i want bobby to want to see me....like not feel like it's a 'chore'...or like he is obligated to see me...i want him to have fun...i need to relax and have fun with our relationship.  It is not a bad relationship...it could be worse...i think that i need to just chill...yes he will be leaving tomorrow to south texas (which I am going to miss him a lot) but i need to have some fun with my friends and not mope around just cause he's not going to be by my side...i will still feel his love...i know that he will think about me...and i know that he is going to miss me...welp...until tomorrow we'll see how it goes after lunch...hopefully he won't make me mad today, or you know what?  I ain't gonna let him make me mad...enjoy this love one day at a time

Well I just am going to jump into this thing they call "live journal".

I am so confused, I don't know what to feel... If I do this, long time consequences could occur, that's what he told me "i meant everything I said"... well that meant that we are in for a long life together, I care for the both of them I really do...Love...I love him....which one you ask?  THE ONE AND ONLY...the one that has been in my life for about a year and a half...this is what it feels like...i don't want to lose what i have with him or the other guy, i care immensely about the both of them...i really do...why do we have to banned from each other...it's so childish...he's the other best friend (C.C)...you are...please don't be mad...I just don't want to lose "the other best friend", he means alot to me C.C., when we were talking about it last nite, I was referred to "his brown eyed doll"... i really wish he could hear that song C.C.

"your'e his brown eyed doll, at least that's what he told you, his words make you feel small, you're his brown eyed doll, at least that's what he told you, he lifts you up to fall..."  

"his brown eyed doll is blue...."
